## Survey [/surveys/{id}]

### Get Survey [GET]

You may get a survey using this action, unique identifier for survey is passed via 
path in URL

+ Parameters
    + id (number, required, `1`)

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Attributes (Survey)
    
    + Body
            
