### Delete a survey [DELETE]

You may use this action to delete a survey.

+ Parameters
    + id (number, required, `1`)
    
+ Response 204

# Data Structures

## Survey (object)

- id (number, required)
- title (string, required)
- description (string)
- questions (array[Question], required)
- created_by (string, required)
- create_date (string, required)


## Question (object)

- text (string, required)
- choices (array[Choice], required)

## Choice (object)

- text (string, required)
- votes: `0` (number, required)